snippet: After a year of controversies and the firing of its coach, Yale nears the end of another season of adversity, only this time with a banged-up team.
abstract: Yale football team, who lost three quarterbacks to injury against Penn in October, will finish last in the league regardless of outcome of upcoming game against rival Harvard.
lead_paragraph: After a year of controversies and the firing of its coach, Yale nears the end of another season of adversity, only this time with a banged-up team.

headline.seo: Yale Keeps Taking Hits, but a New Set of Them
